sort of struggle in this regard.

116
00:06:01,323 --> 00:06:03,465
Also, I often feel like Chinese-speaking regions

117
00:06:03,545 --> 00:06:07,107
are not that well understood by people when I travel abroad.

118
00:06:09,308 --> 00:06:11,730
And it goes without saying that I was greatly inspired

119
