by the Arabic crash course that Rami gave us in GDC 15.

120
00:06:17,883 --> 00:06:21,424
Now let's just dive into some of the actual examples in games.

121
00:06:21,944 --> 00:06:25,345
And for the first example, I want to pull up The Witness.

122
00:06:26,265 --> 00:06:29,105
So actually for The Witness, I am

123
00:06:29,185 --> 00:06:34,087
going to talk about three different issues

124
00:06:34,147 --> 00:06:35,727
of different complexities in it.

125
00:06:36,287 --> 00:06:39,368
The first example here actually is very, very straightforward.

126
00:06:39,908 --> 00:06:43,309
You see five menu buttons in the traditional Chinese version

127
00:06:43,409 --> 00:06:44,189
on a screenshot here.

128
00:06:46,145 --> 00:06:50,609
The first button in English is load a game.

129
00:06:51,530 --> 00:06:55,093
And then the traditional Chinese look like this one.

130
00:06:55,193 --> 00:06:58,376
So if we take that button text in the traditional Chinese

131
00:06:58,396 --> 00:07:00,978
version and translate it back into English for you to

132
00:07:00,998 --> 00:07:04,261
understand, it then becomes download a game.

133
00:07:05,435 --> 00:07:08,978
So if you play The Witness in traditional Chinese,

134
00:07:09,038 --> 00:07:11,460
this really sticks out like a sore thumb.

135
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,621
The game was seven years in the making

136
00:07:13,761 --> 00:07:16,243
and very deliberate and dedicated in all kinds of ways.

137
00:07:17,324 --> 00:07:19,586
Yet the translation people make this kind of mistakes

138
00:07:19,686 --> 00:07:21,947
and the original developer have no way to double check that.

139
00:07:24,229 --> 00:07:26,410
It just feel like the movie Titanic's night sky

140
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:29,312
if you get the Neil Dickerson, Tyson and Jim Cameron joke.

