884
00:53:10,798 --> 00:53:17,182
And I think they are the crucial parts of innovation in games as art and games as media.

885
00:53:17,302 --> 00:53:20,705
So we can have more and more exciting new games in the future.

886
00:53:21,960 --> 00:53:27,323
Every time I come to GDC, I'm always so impressed with the

887
00:53:27,863 --> 00:53:29,924
